VoiceVault,is,software,that,uses,an,individual,s,vocal,characteristics,for,biometric,identity,verification,over,the,phone,web,or,via,mobile,and,smartphone,applications,The,VoiceVault,Fusion,API,is,implemented,as,a,REST,based,XML,service,exposing,the,most,common,VoiceVault,operations,that,drive,user,enrollment,and,verification,processes,Users,can,register,for,the,developer,program,on,the,VoiceVault,website,for,free,access,to,their,API